%h1 This is the Spin show page
%h2 It will inlude all 24 shots in the spin, and display them in viewer
%h3 it also allows the owner of the spin access to edit or delete the spin. if logged in.
=image_tag @spin.shot1

- if user_signed_in?
  - if @spin.user_id == current_user.id
    = link_to "Edit", edit_spin_path(@spin)
    = link_to "Delete", spin_path(@spin), method: :delete, data: { confirm: "Delete Spin?" }

